A BIT ABOUT DENIS ŠAGOV

Denis Sagov was just a child when they first dreamt of becoming a professional Model. This was my motivation to make my body better and stronger. Ever determined and never willing to give up on the dream and profession they loved, Denis Šagov sacrificed much, enduring times of challenge and hardship, in order to earn their reputation in the world.
